rest.sql_statement: SELECT line,vt_line,publishing_name,published_externally,name AS lsmName,area,tile,objective AS objectiveName,effector,cv1.display_name AS age,cv2.display_name AS gender,mounting_protocol,alps_release,workstation_sample_id AS sampleId FROM image_data_mv i JOIN cv_term_vw cv1 ON (cv1.cv_term=i.age AND cv1.cv='age_remap') JOIN cv_term_vw cv2 ON (cv2.cv_term=i.gender AND cv2.cv='gender_remap') AND to_publish='Y'
